.TH LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-BOTH-RESERVES-SKEWNESS-MONTHLY 1
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-both-reserves-skewness-monthly \- monthly skewness of both channel reserves
.SH SYNOPSIS
lightning channel-both-reserves-skewness-monthly
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the monthly skewness of both channel reserves in millisatoshis.
.SH OUTPUT
JSON object with key \fBboth_reserves_skewness_monthly_msat\fR.
